    "suggested a unique Multi-Modal Knowledge-aware Hierarchical Attention Network (MKHAN) to efficiently leverage a multi-modal knowledge graph (MKG) for explainable medical question answering [17].",
    "However, these approaches are often tailored to specific use cases, lacking the generalizability required for broader document interaction tasks.",
